

Install required software
--------------------------

Before starting the buildout process, the following software needs to be installed


python (2.6/2.7)
python-dev
libxml2-dev
libxslt-dev
java 1.6 (Oracle SDK) (VIVO does not work with OpenJDK or Java 1.7)
apache ant (1.8 or higher)
mysql 5.1 or higher
Oracle instantclient

Configure MySQL
---------------
# for the correct user/password/dbname, look at the buildout file

CREATE DATABASE vivo CHARACTER SET utf8;
GRANT ALL ON vivo.* TO 'vivo'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';

Configure Oracle
----------------

Install Oracle instantclient (download from oracle)
Before running the buildout export the paths:

export ORACLE_HOME=/opt/oracle/instantclient_11_2
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/oracle/instantclient_11_2

Running Bootstrap
-----------------
sudo pip install -U distribute
python bootstrap.py
./bin/buildout

Starting Vivo
-------------

Vivo runs under supervisor daemon. Start the daemon with:

./bin/supervisord

Restart / check status with

./bin/supervisorctl

